times.com/1994/07/29/nyregion/president-to-step-down-at-long-island-rail-road.html|title=President to Step Down At Long Island Rail Road|date=1994-07-29|work=The New York Times|access-date=|url-status=live|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331}}</ref>\n*Samuel Hui, CTO of [[Hong Kong Broadband Network]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.humanresourcesonline.net/from-intern-to-leader-samuel-huis-journey-at-hkbn/|title=From intern to leader: Samuel Hui's journey at HKBN|last=Blain|first=Robert|date=2020-02-24|website=Human Resources|language=en-US|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n*[[Kumar Iyer]], Chief Economist of the British [[Foreign and Commonwealth Office]]\n*[[Tom James]], British rower and Olympic gold medalist\n*Andrew Kuritzkes, Chief Risk Officer of [[State Street Corporation]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.crunchbase.com/person/andrew-kuritzkes|title=Andrew Kuritzkes - Executive Vice President and Chief Risk Officer @ State Street|last=|first=|date=|website=Crunchbase|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n* [[Richard Lui]], American journalist and [[MSNBC]] news anchor<ref>{{cite web|url=http://past.naaapconvention.org/2012/NAAAP100/RichardLui.aspx|title=2012 NAAAP 100 Winners|last=|first=|date=|website=NAAAP Convention|publisher=|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170403112227/http://past.naaapconvention.org/2012/NAAAP100/RichardLui.aspx|archive-date=April 3, 2017|accessdate=}}</ref>\n*[[Jim Manzi (software entrepreneur)|Jim Manzi]], co-founder of [[Applied Predictive Technologies]]\n*[[Christopher Meyer (author)|Christopher Meyer]], founder of [[Monitor Deloitte]]\n* [[Nigel Morris]], co-founder of [[Capital One]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.insidearm.com/news/00039118-nigel-morris-co-founder-of-capital-one-jo/|title=Nigel Morris, co-founder of Capital One, Joins TDX Group Board of Directors|last=|first=|date=2013-02-19|website=Inside Arm|publisher=|url-status=live|arch